snippet.title: Sheepong : Match-3 Adventure
snippet.description:
Play on Facebook : https://apps.facebook.com/sheepong
Play on iOS : https://apple.co/3aUHIJA
Play on Android : https://bit.ly/2xxbKo5
Play on Amazon : https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08GLW815P/

SHEEPONG'S NEW JOURNEY BEGINS!
Sheepong, a teenage sheep, is eager to start his adventure and explore a whole world to save his mother taken by bad wolves. Match 3 or more blocks on the boards to make a match, learn new rules of creating and mixing specials, meet new enemies and prepare your mind for new exciting missions! A true FUN start here where this game begins.
